extends layout

block content
	section#hero-cover.cover.height-50.imagebg.parallax.text-center(data-overlay="5")
		//- background image
		div.background-image-holder(style="background-image: url(/img/header/loans-personal.jpg); background-position:center bottom; opacity: 1;") 
			//-background image for smaller devices
			img.attachment-full.size-full(width="1600" height="1067" src="/img/header/loans-personal.jpg" alt="" srcset="/img/header/loans-personal.jpg 1600w, /img/header/loans-personal.jpg 300w, /img/header/loans-personal.jpg 768w, /img/header/loans-personal.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px")
		div#hero-content.container.pos-vertical-center
			div.row.text-center
				div.col-sm-12
					h1 Personal Loans
			div.vc_empty_space(style="height: 32px")
				span.vc_empty_space_inner
	section
		div.container
			div.row
				div.col-md-12.text-center
					a.btn.btn--primary-2(href="/loans")
						i.icon.icon--xs.fa.fa-arrow-left.color--white(style="margin-right:20px;")
						span.btn__text Back to Loans
	section
		div.container

			div.row.margin-bottom-30.text-center

				div.col-md-12
					h4.color--primary Line of Credit
					a.btn.btn--primary-2(href="#")
						span.btn__text Apply Now
			
			div.row
				div.col-md-12
					p.
						With low interest rates, flexible repayment terms and as borrowed funds are repaid each month, they become available to borrow again! One great use of your Line of Credit is for Overdraft Protection for your Checking Account. You can avoid the expense and embarrassment of a bounced check by setting up an Overdraft Line of Credit. If your account is overdrawn, we have free overdraft protection with no minimum dollar amount. Or, when unexpected expenses or emergencies arise, a Line of Credit provides a source of funds when you need it.

			hr
			
			div.row.margin-bottom-30.text-center

				div.col-md-12
					h4.color--primary Secured Loans
					a.btn.btn--primary-2(href="#")
						span.btn__text Apply Now
			
			div.row
				div.col-md-12
					p.
						As a great low-rate loan, you can use your funds that are on deposit in your Tulare Federal Savings Account or Certificate as collateral. We simply add a small percentage to your savings rate, so while you pay off your loan, your Savings or Certificate Account continues to earn dividends.


			hr

			div.row.margin-bottom-30.text-center

				div.col-md-12
					h4.color--primary Signature Loans
					a.btn.btn--primary-2(href="#")
						span.btn__text Apply Now
			
			div.row
				div.col-md-12
					p.
						A variety of personal loans are available to members who need additional cash. An unsecured Signature Loan can provide a specific dollar amount for a set period of time to be used for any reason and requires no collateral â€“ just your signature based on your credit history.

			